text: Angelucci can be: * Orfeo Angelucci, mid-1950s contactee who claimed to be in contact with extraterrestrials * Gilberto Angelucci, a retired Venezuelan football goalkeeper * Jonathan Angelucci, an Australian football (soccer) player * Liborio Angelucci (1746–1811), an Italian physician and politician * Marc Angelucci (1968–2020), an American attorney and murder victim
title: Angelucci
